        {
            "title": "元朗33歲男捱斬面遭割傷 獨行刀手逞兇後逃去",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5100f849d7123ee282ba622195fd1b51/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022004521284700.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>元朗發生斬人案。周三晚上（19日）11時40分，一名33歲男子在錦田公路吉慶圍180號，遭一名戴口罩惡漢用一把長約20厘米的利刀揮斬，當場面部被割傷，刀手得手後逃去無踪。事主負傷自行報案，獲送博愛醫院治理。\n\n</p>\n<p>警員在案發現場一帶兜截，惟無發現，案件暫列「傷人」處理，交元朗警區刑事調查隊第10隊跟進，正追緝一名年約30至40歲男子。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053811/即時-港聞-元朗33歲男捱斬面遭割傷-獨行刀手逞兇後逃去",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-20 05:01:27",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
